{"tid":735400,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[CS1.6] Base Builder 6.5 試開","createTime":"2018-07-09T12:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T04:25:40.000Z","uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"22148ee2f453377bac808f28577a25c5c21f95f8","tid":735400,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cache.gametracker.com/server_info/66.42.48.13:27015/banner_560x95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.gametracker.com%2Fserver_info%2F66.42.48.13%3A27015%2Fbanner_560x95.png&h=81e16aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBase Builder 介紹：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?t=144287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforums.alliedmods.net%2Fshowthread.php%3Ft%3D144287&d=EnxnWlTrMMSlO8XdiPT%2Ft0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=80627382\" target=\"_blank\">https://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?t=144287</a><br />\n<br />\n後台指令<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">bind +use &lt;key&gt;</span></strong> (grabs selected object while pressed)<br />\n<br />\n可用指令：<br />\n/guns = Opens the guns menu (CTs can change guns until build time is up)<br />\n/respawn = Zombie command to respawn (to fix bad spawning or stick)<br />\n/fixspawn = Respawns survivor during build phase (fixes if they stick themselves)<br />\n/help = Displays help HUD<br />\n/rules = Displays rules HUD<br />\n/round = Displays current round (ex. Round 3 of 4)<br />\n<br />\n可以喺下面download埋Base Builder本身嘅sounds同models 進入server就只需要download個map<br />\n然後放落cstrike個file就OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nModels: <a href=\"https://forums.alliedmods.net/attachment.php?attachmentid=80652&amp;d=1294911659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforums.alliedmods.net%2Fattachment.php%3Fattachmentid%3D80652%26d%3D1294911659&d=EnxnWlTrMMSlO8XdiPT%2Ft0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a81d0295\" target=\"_blank\">https://forums.alliedmods.net/attachment.php?attachmentid=80652&amp;d=1294911659</a><br />\nSounds: <a href=\"https://forums.alliedmods.net/attachment.php?attachmentid=80653&amp;d=1294911688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforums.alliedmods.net%2Fattachment.php%3Fattachmentid%3D80653%26d%3D1294911688&d=EnxnWlTrMMSlO8XdiPT%2Ft0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=9296630e\" target=\"_blank\">https://forums.alliedmods.net/attachment.php?attachmentid=80653&amp;d=1294911688</a><br />\n<br />\nIP: 66.42.48.13:27015<br />\n由於只係試開階段 所以maxplayer暫時set咗喺16人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後可能會開到32人"},{"pid":"2479210ff691318494c7abaf8dab1df5ab72af98","tid":735400,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T13:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edba308a160698e0ce6fcccd073559c1a71dfbe5","tid":735400,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T13:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7311bcb962352d39c2d6a504ccbd86d8b311bc","tid":735400,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259f5f10f7a3fd1b1bd4d298d64378d01abb84b2","tid":735400,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1e69d2f70780c5e568cadf337de3787b969af3","tid":735400,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T04:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}